{"data":[{"id":560977893,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"f78a0d17005e77eb4196aaee83e56586","url_token":"darkkiva","name":"Darkkiva","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-37c1e5852b075b38b36cac322968778e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-37c1e5852b075b38b36cac322968778e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/f78a0d17005e77eb4196aaee83e56586","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":2,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560977893","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545903888,"updated_time":1546315887,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":14,"comment_count":8,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e不请自来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baijiahao.baidu.com/s%3Fid%3D1582129353047847355%26wfr%3Dspider%26for%3Dpc%26isFailFlag%3D1\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttps://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003ebaijiahao.baidu.com/s?\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003eid=1582129353047847355\u0026amp;wfr=spider\u0026amp;for=pc\u0026amp;isFailFlag=1\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ellipsis\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先表明一下立场，我是不相信题主已经证明哥猜的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想告诉题主的是，在知乎上问这样的问题而收到这么多的嘲讽，是一件很正常，而且很正确的事。但是，题主你要明白，这些嘲讽你的言论真的是出于善意的心。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哥德巴赫猜想被称为“数学皇冠上的明珠”，这么多年来有这么多学者耗费无数时间与心血发起挑战，但都无功而返。目前，若是有一位高中生却说证明了哥猜，这算是对这些学者和数学本身的一种冒犯了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我刚刚看到这个问题的时候也感受到了一丝愤怒。作为一名大二狗，刚刚和复变积变试卷硬剛一场，正感叹自己知识水平有待提高，就看到一个所有学者都对其心怀尊敬的事物被答主用来当做了获得名利的筹码，这已经是很让人倍感羞辱的事情了。（更别提还只是为了高校的通行证而不是学术）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不管前面自称题主老师的答主是不是真的，从题目猜测题主应该是高中生，正在为高考发愁，这时可能是错误理解了哥猜的思想妄论证明了哥猜并且在视野已知的最高平台——知乎寻问能否借所谓“证明哥猜”的学术成果获得清北资格。但是，作为学术水平较高的知乎平台，我们不会盲目鼓励题主你的行为或诋毁你已做的努力，而是努力告诉你你的视野太过狭隘、知识水平也根本不足以解决内涵深邃的高等数学问题，希望你不要轻视数学本身、不要轻视知识以及为知识奋斗中的我们大家。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（PS：我本人非常反感欺骗他人信任之人，如果发现题主真实的目的是骗热度炒作自己，我相信会有无数知乎群众顺着WIFI过去砍人的←_←，要真是这样请各位知乎er告诉我题主坐标，虽然没有八百狙，但是歼星炮应该勉强能用用(●—●)）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e没人看但是更新(눈_눈)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e好啦好啦，大家记得取关题主啦，这个证明就是个笑话(●—●)\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"不请自来。\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baijiahao.baidu.com/s%3Fid%3D1582129353047847355%26wfr%3Dspider%26for%3Dpc%26isFailFlag%3D1\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttps://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003ebaijiahao.baidu.com/s?\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003eid=1582129353047847355\u0026amp;wfr=spider\u0026amp;for=pc\u0026amp;isFailFlag=1\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ellipsis\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e首先表明一下立场，我是不相信题主已经证明哥猜的。我想告诉题主的是，在知乎上问这样的问题而收到这么多的嘲讽，是一件很正常，而且很正确的事。但是，题主你要明白，这些嘲讽你的言论真的是出于善意的心。哥德巴赫猜想被称…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"rela